2. cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a communication protocol for relaying, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - Similar to cs.COMM, the paper discusses a communication protocol for relaying, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the performance of a system (relay system) over a fading channel, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - Although less likely, the paper could fall under the domain of multiagent systems as it discusses a protocol for relaying information between multiple agents (source, relay, and destination).
